description: QUOVIO 49T trolley is airline carry-on compatible and lightweight, so you, and your gear, will reach your destination with ease. But that doesn't mean it's short on space; there's plenty of room for a DSLR with attached zoom lens, as well as an additional zoom and other lenses, flash, and other accessories. A well-padded laptop compartment keeps your personal computer safe and nearby. Traveling without your gear? Simply remove QUOVIO 49T's customizable interior for use as a roomy carry-on bag. A convenient and inconspicuously stowed tripod holder with Quick Adjustment Straps makes bringing your trusted camera support along for the ride quicker and simpler than ever.
title: VANGUARD Quovio 49T Carry-On Compatible Lightweight Trolley (Black)
